Package org.team5940.pantry.processing_network

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Network
    A Network is a thread that updates a set of Nodes.
    Node
    A Node is a component of a single Network.
    NodeGroup
    A NodeGroup is used to allow easy creation for a set of Nodes, such as a Group of Motors.
    ProcessingNetworkUtils
    Various utilities that Nodes may need to use.
    ValueNode<T>
    A Node that stores data of type T.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    IllegalUpdateThreadException
    An exception to indicate that you are attempting to update a Node from a Thread other than its Network.
